title: Stephen A. reacts to the Clippers acquiring Eric Bledsoe after trading Beverley, Rondo and Oturu
author: ESPN
description:
Stephen A. reacts to the Clippers acquiring Eric Bledsoe after trading Beverley, Rondo and Oturu
Stephen A. Smith and Max Kellerman react to the LA Clippers trading Patrick Beverley, Rajon Rondo and Daniel Oturu to the Memphis Grizzlies in exchange for Eric Bledsoe.
